            . I am a pawbroker. I took a decanter in pledge; on the 2d of August the prisoner came, and had more advanced upon it,</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170917-220-person1502">
                  STEPHEN 
                  TANNER
               <interp inst="t18170917-220-person1502" type="surname" value="TANNER"></interp>
