                     <interp inst="t18170917-220-person1502" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 6th of September I apprehended the prisoner, and found forty-six duplicates on hm-three of them were relating to the property.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner called the following Witnesses:</p>
               <p>EMANUEL WOOLFE. I have worked for the prosecutor. When I have applied to him to pay me my wages, he used to send me to pledge things to get the money. He is a common thief!</p>
               <p>JAMES LACEY. I worked for the prosecutor - he used to ask me to pledge things.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170917-220-person1503">
